creature like the minotaurs

00:12:30.730 --> 00:12:32.550 align:middle line:10%
or the centaur, et cetera.

00:12:32.550 --> 00:12:34.680 align:middle line:84%
The mixed creatures
were made by the gods.

00:12:34.680 --> 00:12:36.510 align:middle line:84%
The gods were the
extraterrestrials.

00:12:36.510 --> 00:12:38.760 align:middle line:84%
They had the
genetical knowledge.

00:12:38.760 --> 00:12:42.270 align:middle line:84%
Now the gods ordered
to the humans,

00:12:42.270 --> 00:12:45.000 align:middle line:84%
you are not allowed
to chase, to kill

00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:47.490 align:middle line:84%
some of these mixed
creatures, because they

00:12:47.490 --> 00:12:49.360 align:middle line:90%
want to observe them.

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:51.270 align:middle line:90%
The gods disappeared one day.

00:12:51.270 --> 00:12:53.220 align:middle line:84%
The mixed creatures
were still there.

00:12:53.220 --> 00:12:55.890 align:middle line:84%
Now the humans were still
afraid of the mixed creatures.

00:12:55.890 --> 00:12:58.110 align:middle line:84%
They waited until
the mixed creatures

00:12:58.110 --> 00:13:00.720 align:middle line:90%
died in a natural way.

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:02.190 align:middle line:90%
Now they were dead.

00:13:02.190 --> 00:13:05.290 align:middle line:84%
And now they made
gigantic sarcophaguses,

00:13:05.290 --> 00:13:08.160 align:middle line:84%
the stones from Aswan,
underground tunnels.

00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:11.940 align:middle line:84%
They broke the bones
of the mixed creatures.

00:13:11.940 --> 00:13:15.660 align:middle line:84%
They put it into these gigantic
sarcophaguses, covered it

00:13:15.660 --> 00:13:17.640 align:middle line:90%
with bitumen, liquid bitumen.

00:13:17.640 --> 00:13:20.160 align:middle line:84%
Bitumen, when it's hot,
it stinks terribly.

00:13:20.160 --> 00:13:21.210 align:middle line:90%
You can use it.

00:13:21.210 --> 00:13:23.730 align:middle line:90%
And put a lid of 40 tons of it.

00:13:23.730 --> 00:13:28.020 align:middle line:84%
It was not the reborn,
it was the contrary.

00:13:28.020 --> 00:13:32.880 align:middle line:84%
These monsters should
never be reborn again.

00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:35.220 align:middle line:84%
That's why the
gigantic sarcophagus.

00:13:35.220 --> 00:13:39.570 align:middle line:84%
So today, if we
simply take one bone,

00:13:39.570 --> 00:13:42.780 align:middle line:84%
our geneticists are so
fantastic in their knowledge

00:13:42.780 --> 00:13:46.500 align:middle line:84%
they could very easily
prove that this is not

00:13:46.500 --> 00:13:49.380 align:middle line:90%
the normal DNA of a creature.

00:13:49.380 --> 00:13:52.290 align:middle line:84%
It was easy to prove
that it is the product

00:13:52.290 --> 00:13:53.670 align:middle line:90%
of a genetical design.

00:13:53.670 --> 00:13:55.150 align:middle line:90%
It's mixed creatures.

00:13:55.150 --> 00:13:58.890 align:middle line:84%
The problem is just no
geneticist will do the job.

00:13:58.890 --> 00:14:02.280 align:middle line:84%
I know one of the geneticist who
said Eric, I will do the job.

00:14:02.280 --> 00:14:04.874 align:middle line:84%
But once, when he come
to the result, here

00:14:04.874 --> 00:14:06.540 align:middle line:84%
we have the product
of a mixed creature,

00:14:06.540 --> 00:14:08.460 align:middle line:90%
