00:14:08.460 --> 00:14:09.480 align:middle line:90%
Why not?

00:14:09.480 --> 00:14:11.070 align:middle line:90%
The time is not ripe.

00:14:11.070 --> 00:14:13.920 align:middle line:84%
His colleagues would
block him, he said.

00:14:13.920 --> 00:14:15.150 align:middle line:90%
What are you doing here?

00:14:15.150 --> 00:14:16.470 align:middle line:90%
This is impossible in our time.

00:14:16.470 --> 00:14:18.011 align:middle line:84%
You cannot come with
mixed creatures.

00:14:18.011 --> 00:14:19.680 align:middle line:84%
As soon as you have
mixed creatures,

00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:21.840 align:middle line:84%
you prove extraterrestrials,
because only

00:14:21.840 --> 00:14:25.630 align:middle line:84%
the extraterrestrials had
the knowledge in genetics.

00:14:25.630 --> 00:14:27.766 align:middle line:90%
And so the story ends.

